Here's probably a good one, it's a mega scream which buffs my friendly units,

203
00:10:17,877 --> 00:10:22,183
so I would already know that indicates that I would have to create that kind of scream later on as well.

204
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:26,272
And also put a note that it can attack from distance

205
00:10:26,272 --> 00:10:28,494
with a fireball, so I probably have to think

