00:10:28,494 --> 00:10:30,555
from the very start about my distance as well

207
00:10:30,555 --> 00:10:32,797
and what that brings to the table.

208
00:10:32,797 --> 00:10:35,819
And then on the right here on the left page,

209
00:10:35,819 --> 00:10:38,300
you can see how attack paints green

210
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:40,082
and how many variations I aim to do.

