00:10:40,082 --> 00:10:43,804
And that equals total amount of 42 sound effects

212
00:10:43,804 --> 00:10:45,986
in this case, and this is a good indication.

213
00:10:45,986 --> 00:10:47,987
I can put that on a timeline

