00:10:47,987 --> 00:10:49,308
and plan my time accordingly.

215
00:10:50,309 --> 00:10:55,731
And on the right, I think that's a very, for myself, it's very important, is the potential

216
00:10:55,731 --> 00:11:00,673
recordings I'm going to do, also the potential source I'm going to look at to just buy from

217
00:11:00,673 --> 00:11:02,074
other libraries out there.

